From: Paul Bastide <pbastide@redhat.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 16:31:25 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] MULTIARCH-5768: Migrate the power libvirt CI to use
 cis.ibm.net

Signed-off-by: Paul Bastide <pbastide@redhat.com>
---
